[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":177},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fgit\u002F20220220\u002F2457085338\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fgit\u002F20220220\u002F2457085338\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fgit\u002F20220220\u002F2457085338\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fgit\u002F20220220\u002F2457085338\u002F":154,"related:\u002Fgit\u002F20220220\u002F2457085338\u002F":163},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2022\u002F02\u002F20\u002Forganize-github-stars-with-tags\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":136,"date":137,"description":18,"extension":138,"lang":139,"meta":140,"navigation":141,"path":142,"readingMinutes":143,"seo":144,"standalone":145,"stem":146,"tags":147,"tldr":151,"updated":151,"url":152,"__hash__":153},"content\u002FGit\u002FGitHub-替自己-Star-過的專案加上-Tag-吧！.md","GitHub 替自己 Star 過的專案加上 Tag 吧！","2457085338",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":130},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,32,35,38,44,47,52,55,61,64,70,73,79,82,88,91,97,100,103,109,112,118,121,127],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"相信身為工程師的你一定曾經在 GitHub 上替自己喜歡的專案給一個 Star，但是當我們 Star 的專案越來越多的時候，要回頭找相關的專案反而很麻煩，因此這一篇就來介紹一下該怎麼處理自己按過的 Star 專案囉。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"stars-lists","Stars Lists",[16,24,25],{},"GitHub 後來針對 Star 頁面增加了一個 Stars Lists 功能，你只需要到你的個人首頁，然後點一下上方頁籤 Stars，就可以看到 Stars Lists",[16,27,28],{},[29,30],"img",{"alt":22,"src":31},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.02.22.png",[16,33,34],{},"而 Stars Lists 就是我們這次一次的重點功能。這個功能其實就是 tag 分類",[16,36,37],{},"那麼該怎麼使用呢？首先你先點一下 Create list 按鈕",[16,39,40],{},[29,41],{"alt":42,"src":43},"Create list","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202202202204.png",[16,45,46],{},"接下來會有兩個欄位，分別是 Name this list 與 write a description",[16,48,49],{},[29,50],{"alt":42,"src":51},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.04.31.png",[16,53,54],{},"那我這邊就示範建立一個 Vue 相關的 Tag",[16,56,57],{},[29,58],{"alt":59,"src":60},"Vue Tag","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.07.36.png",[16,62,63],{},"建立好後我們會先被導向到這個 Tag 的內頁，當你看到這個頁面就恭喜你建立好了",[16,65,66],{},[29,67],{"alt":68,"src":69},"建立成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.08.29.png",[16,71,72],{},"接下來該如何把自己按過 Star 的專案放進來到這邊呢？回到 Stars 頁面，然後找到你要分類的 Star 專案，點一下小箭頭(more)，你就可以看到剛剛新增的 Vue 選項，把它打勾即可",[16,74,75],{},[29,76],{"alt":77,"src":78},"新增 tag","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.09.45.png",[16,80,81],{},"當然如果你建立很多 Tag 的話，也可以複選",[16,83,84],{},[29,85],{"alt":86,"src":87},"複選","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.11.24.png",[16,89,90],{},"幫 Star 的專案加上 Tag 後，之後你就可以在 Stars 上方的列表直接管理你有 Star 過的專案",[16,92,93],{},[29,94],{"alt":95,"src":96},"Lists","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.14.49.png",[16,98,99],{},"這對於喜好分類的人來講是一個福音 RRRRR",[16,101,102],{},"當然你也可以在 Star 專案之前就先做好 Tag 好了",[16,104,105],{},[29,106],{"alt":107,"src":108},"先 Tag 再說","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.16.40.png",[16,110,111],{},"除此之外這個功能還有一個優勢，你可以用於管理 Private 的專案，因為被加上 Tag 的專案並不會呈現在列表上的，例如...我把我的 Private 的 Hexo 系統加入到 test 這個 Tag 中",[16,113,114],{},[29,115],{"alt":116,"src":117},"test","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202202202219.png",[16,119,120],{},"那麼其他人就只會看到這個 Tag 但不會看到內容",[16,122,123],{},[29,124],{"alt":125,"src":126},"空白內容","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-02-20%2022.20.16.png",[16,128,129],{},"如果你跟我一樣從以前就一直在煩惱 Star 可不可以分類這個問題的人，現在可以開心了！因為 GitHub 終於支援啦~~",{"title":131,"searchDepth":132,"depth":132,"links":133},"",2,[134,135],{"id":14,"depth":132,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":132,"text":22},"Git","2022-02-20 21:58:39","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fgit\u002Fgithub-star-tag","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"Git\u002FGitHub-替自己-Star-過的專案加上-Tag-吧！",[148,136,149,150],"GitHub","Star","Star List",null,"\u002Fgit\u002F20220220\u002F2457085338\u002F","02FcUi1MCc3562AY_W7j1WTdZXeFwNh_xcswotNaThU",{"newer":155,"older":159},{"url":156,"title":157,"date":158},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220221\u002F3674730635\u002F","(9)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - Mongoose - Connect MongoDB 與 Schema","2022-02-21 09:00:19",{"url":160,"title":161,"date":162},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20220220\u002F3877598394\u002F","(8)被迫吃芒果的前端工程師 - MongoDB - ODM","2022-02-20 08:47:35",[164,169,173],{"url":165,"title":166,"date":167,"readingMinutes":168},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260226\u002F799954596\u002F","取代 git push --force 更好的方式，git push --force-with-lease","2026-02-26 09:39:40","4",{"url":170,"title":171,"date":172,"readingMinutes":143},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260122\u002F21277993\u002F","Git init 出現 master 分支提示？教你設定預設分支為 main","2026-01-22 16:20:40",{"url":174,"title":175,"date":176,"readingMinutes":168},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260121\u002F2025687513\u002F","Git Worktree 是什麼？一個專案同時跑多個 AI Agent 的秘訣","2026-01-21 16:04:27",1784013081346]